.5 亿元。对此，赛力斯方面解释称，这主要是由于问界 M9 、 M7 等研发投入较高，导致研发费用、人工成本等综合成本较高。同时，为了实现销售上量，公司加大了销售渠道建设和市场营销投入。 《每日经济新闻》记者查阅赛力斯历年年度报告发现，赛力斯的亏损始于 2020 年，到 2023 年累计亏损金额约 98.35 亿元。 国信证券研报认为，赛力斯近几年持续研发投入，专注打造产品，历经近四年亏损承压，2024 年一季度实现净利润扭亏为盈，有望开启新一轮上行周期。4 年亏损近百亿，赛力斯今年一季度扭亏为盈，问界车型销量贡献度超九成"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c854c0e2f89d65587905b2afdd0adf96_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "132 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655212254"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I95fd+qyr6fdDEAMaCTEwNzg4MDI3NyCerOaxBjAAOEtABXIJNjU1MjEyMjU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1715098912.165327", "card_id": "Q_653586031", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我想知道如果有一个女生不相信所有男性怎么办，包括她的爸爸，怎样才能让她相信我呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653586031"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I95fd+qyr6fdDEAMaCTEwNzUxOTI0MyCC84+xBjAAOFJABnIJNjUzNTg2MDMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1715098912.165582", "card_id": "Q_654418133", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 106}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一旦以色列全面入侵拉法和约旦河西岸，埃及、黎巴嫩和约旦进行地面军事干涉的可能性有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text